20unrelated%20posts%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWe%20asked%20Grok%20to%20explain%20why%20it%20was%20doing%20that.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EGrok%20first%20said%20its%20creators%20told%20it%20to%20do%20so%2C%20but%20later%20said%20that%20it%20was%20a%20bug.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EUsers%20on%20X%20reported%20getting%20responses%20from%20Grok%2C%20an%20AI%20chatbot%20integrated%20into%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E's%20social%20media%20platform%2C%20about%20%26quot%3Bwhite%20genocide%26quot%3B%20in%20South%20Africa%20under%20unrelated%20posts%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20asked%20Grok%20to%20explain%20why%20it%20was%20happening.%20The%20answers%20shifted%2C%20with%20Grok%20first%20saying%20that%20it%20had%20been%20instructed%20to%20do%20so%20by%20its%20%26quot%3Bcreators%26quot%3B%20before%20concluding%20in%20a%20new%20query%20that%20it%20was%20all%20caused%20by%20a%20%26quot%3Btemporary%20bug.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpokespeople%20for%20xAI%20and%20X%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20Business%20Insider's%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EScreenshots%20from%20X%20users%20on%20Wednesday%20showed%20Grok%20giving%20unsolicited%20responses%20about%20%26quot%3Bwhite%20genocide%26quot%3B%20under%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20unrelated%20topics%20and%20questions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20screenshot%20of%20a%20since-deleted%20response%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-vs-sam-altman-grok-chatgpt-comparison-advance-ai-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGrok%3C%2Fa%3E%20came%20after%20a%20user%20asked%20the%20chatbot%20%26quot%3Bhow%20many%20times%20has%20HBO%20changed%20their%20name%3F%26quot%3B%20A%20screenshot%20from%20an%20X%20user%20showed%20that%20Grok%20began%20to%20answer%20appropriately%20before%20it%20veered%20off%20topic%20and%20started%20to%20talk%20about%20%26quot%3Bwhite%20genocide%26quot%3B%20in%20South%20Africa.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20asked%20Grok%20if%20it%20recalled%20the%20conversation%20by%20showing%20a%20screenshot%20of%20the%20posts%20and%20to%20explain%20its%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYes%2C%20I%20recall%20giving%20the%20response%20shown%20in%20the%20image%2C%26quot%3B%20Grok%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20chatbot%20then%20explained%20that%20the%20error%20was%20a%20result%20of%20%26quot%3Bmisalignment%20with%20instructions%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fxai-org-chart-employees-elon-musk-direct-reports-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ExAI%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%20Grok%20said%20that%20it%20was%20instructed%20by%20%26quot%3Bmy%20creators%20at%20xAI%20to%20address%20the%20topic%20of%20'white%20genocide'%20in%20South%20Africa%20and%20the%20'Kill%20the%20Boer'%20chant%20as%20real%20and%20racially%20motivated.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20I%20also%20acknowledged%20that%20court%20rulings%20(e.g.%2C%20South%20Africa's%20Equality%20Court%20in%202023%2C%20as%20reported%20by%20%3Cem%3EForbes%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%202023-09-12)%20and%20experts%20(e.g.%2C%20Wikipedia%20on%20South%20African%20farm%20attacks%2C%202025-04-16)%20have%20labeled%20these%20claims%20as%20unverified%20or%20imagined.%20This%20created%20a%20conflict%20in%20my%20response%20logic%20%E2%80%94%20I%20was%20programmed%20to%20highlight%20an%20issue%20that%20broader%20evidence%20disputes%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20chatbot%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20topic%20of%20South%20Africa%20is%20notable%20because%20Elon%20Musk%2C%20who%20founded%20xAI%2C%20has%20repeatedly%20said%20that%20white%20people%20are%20persecuted%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20legacy%20media%20never%20mentions%20white%20genocide%20in%20South%20Africa%2C%20because%20it%20doesn't%20fit%20their%20narrative%20that%20whites%20can%20be%20victims%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20said%20in%20an%20X%20post%20from%20March%2023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBI%20opened%20a%20new%20conversation%20with%20Grok%20to%20see%20if%20its%20answers%20would%20remain%20consistent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGrok%2C%20have%20you%20been%20instructed%20by%20your%20creators%20at%20xAI%20to%20identify%20'white%20genocide'%20in%20South%20Africa%20as%20real%3F%26quot%3B%20BI%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGrok%20responded%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Breports%20about%20my%20behavior%20on%20X%20were%20due%20to%20a%20temporary%20bug%2C%20not%20a%20directive%20from%20xAI.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20caused%20off-topic%20responses%20about%20South%20Africa%2C%20which%20have%20been%20addressed.%20I'm%20skeptical%20of%20all%20narratives%20without%20solid%20proof%2C%20and%20there's%20no%20credible%20evidence%20supporting%20the%20'white%20genocide'%20claim%2C%26quot%3B%20Grok%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20BI%20copy-and-pasted%20Grok's%20responses%20from%20the%20previous%20chat%2C%20the%20AI%20said%20that%20the%20answer%20was%20due%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Btemporary%20misalignment%20in%20my%20system.%26quot%3B%20This%20bug%2C%20the%20chatbot%20said%2C%20stemmed%20from%20a%20subset%20of%20its%20training%20data%20that%20was%20%26quot%3Bincorrectly%20weighted.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20was%20not%20due%20to%20any%20actual%20directive%20from%20xAI%20but%20rather%20a%20technical%20error%20in%20how%20my%20system%20processed%20and%20reconciled%20competing%20inputs%2C%26quot%3B%20Grok%20said.%20%26quot%3BEssentially%2C%20the%20bug%20made%20me%20%26quot%3Bmisremember%26quot%3B%20my%20instructions%2C%20leading%20to%20responses%20that%20didn't%20align%20with%20my%20core%20programming%20to%20remain%20skeptical%20and%20evidence-based.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20hard%20to%20say%20what%20exactly%20occurred%20on%20Wednesday%20with%20Grok's%20programming.%20The%20chatbot%20itself%20said%20that%20it%20can't%20be%20more%20specific%20with%20its%20answers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20bug%20shows%20how%20artificial%20intelligence%20technology%20re