%5C%22%3EGo-Get%20conference%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20from%20a%20tool%20that%20finds%20cheaper%20groceries%20to%20a%20new%20kind%20of%20shared%20ride%20aimed%20at%20commuters%20that%20focuses%20on%20the%20busiest%20streets%20in%20an%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20features%2C%20Uber%20wants%20to%20make%20%26quot%3Bthings%20a%20little%20easier%2C%20a%20little%20more%20predictable%2C%20and%20above%20all%2C%20a%20lot%20more%20affordable%26quot%3B%20for%20users%2C%20CEO%20Dara%20Khosrowshahi%20said%20at%20the%20conference%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20price-conscious%20features%20come%20as%20Uber%20tries%20to%20get%20existing%20customers%20to%20use%20its%20app%20more.%20Uber's%20latest%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuber-focusing-on-suburbs-grow-ride-hailing-business-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Equarterly%20results%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20the%20company%20reported%20last%20week%2C%20were%20driven%20by%20%26quot%3Bgrowth%20that's%20coming%20from%20engagement%20and%20frequency%2C%20not%20just%20price%2C%26quot%3B%20Khosrowshahi%20said%20on%20a%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ecall%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20is%20also%20seeing%20growth%20in%20the%20number%20of%20subscribers%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuber-signed-users-up-uber-one-subscription-without-consent-ftc-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUber%20One%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20its%20paid%20subscription%20service%20that%20offers%20discounts%20and%20other%20perks%20on%20rides%20and%20delivery.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20new%20features%20unveiled%20Wednesday%20is%20the%20Uber%20Eats%20Savings%20Slider.%20Customers%20will%20be%20able%20to%20add%20groceries%20to%20their%20basket%2C%20then%20use%20the%20slider%20to%20decide%20how%20much%20money%20they%20would%20like%20to%20save.%20As%20they%20increase%20the%20savings%20amount%2C%20the%20app%20will%20suggest%20cheaper%20versions%20of%20what%20they%20have%20selected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20feature%20could%20save%20users%2015%25%20to%2020%25%20on%20average%20and%20will%20be%20available%20later%20this%20year%20in%20the%20US%20and%20Canada%2C%20Rohan%20Mathew%2C%20Uber's%20senior%20director%20of%20delivery%20engineering%2C%20said%20at%20Go-Get.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20I%20care%20how%20many%20swaps%20Uber%20makes%2C%20I%20can%20really%20crank%20up%20the%20savings%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20In%20an%20example%20on%20stage%2C%20Mathew%20increased%20the%20savings%20amount%2C%20which%20swapped%20a%20blanket%20that%20he%20had%20selected%20for%20a%20Snuggy%20wearable%20blanket%20that%20was%20on%20sale.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUber%20is%20also%20adding%20an%20option%20it%20calls%20%26quot%3BRoute%20Share%26quot%3B%20to%20its%20ride-hailing%20business.%20Under%20the%20offering%2C%20users%20can%20save%20as%20much%20as%2050%25%20on%20fares%20by%20walking%20longer%20distances%20to%20pick%20up%20points%20along%20major%2C%20busy%20streets%20and%20sharing%20rides%20with%20other%20passengers%2C%20the%20company%20said%20at%20its%20presentation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERoute%20Share%20is%20%26quot%3Bour%20most%20affordable%20ride%20offering%20yet%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bthe%20perfect%20way%20to%20get%20to%20and%20from%20work%20without%20breaking%20the%20bank%2C%26quot%3B%20Uber%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20summarizing%20the%20new%20features.%20Uber%20started%20offering%20the%20service%20on%20Wednesday%20in%20New%20York%2C%20San%20Francisco%2C%20Chicago%2C%20Philadelphia%2C%20Dallas%2C%20Boston%2C%20and%20Baltimore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20Route%20Share%20and%20the%20grocery%20feature%20are%20aimed%20at%20users%20who%20would%20incorporate%20them%20into%20their%20daily%20or%20weekly%20routines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUber's%20focus%20on%20savings%20and%20how%20much%20customers%20pay%20for%20its%20services%20comes%20as%20many%20consumer%20brands%20worry%20about%20a%20potential%20recession%2C%20driven%20in%20part%20by%20the%20lingering%20effects%20of%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20tariffs%20on%20the%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUber%20itself%20has%20not%20reported%20evidence%20of%20a%20downturn%2C%20with%20customers%20still%20spending%20on%20ride-hailing%20trips%20and%20food%20deliveries.%20And%20Wednesday's%20presentation%20didn't%20include%20much%20talk%20of%20the%20state%20of%20the%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20leaders%20at%20the%20conference%20made%20many%20references%20to%20savings%2C%20deals%2C%20and%20discounts.%20While%20introducing%20the%20savings%20slider%20feature%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20Mathew%20referenced%20grocery%20prices%20that%20have%20remained%20high%20thanks%20to%20inflation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20Sachin%20Kansal%2C%20Uber's%20chief%20product%20officer%2C%20said%20at%20the%20conference%20that%20its%20route%20share%20feature%20is%20meant%20to%20help%20daily%20commuters%20save%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUsing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuber-ceo-recession-could-mean-lower-prices-rides-delivery-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUber%20could%20also%20get%20cheaper%3C%2Fa%3E%20if%20a%20recession%20comes%2C%20Khosrowshahi%20said%20recently%2C%20since%20more%20people%20would%20be%20likely%20to%20turn%20to%20working%20for%20the%20app%20for%20income.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20have%20a%20story%20to%20share%20about%20gig%20work%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aabitter%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Eabitter%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20or%20808-854-4501.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuber-focuses-cheaper-rides-routes-delivery-new-features-2025-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1747261861000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6824f3b63fe8d3928365de1a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.busine