32-e1730993745426.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236398433%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20some%20initial%20reluctance%2C%20Bruce%20Springsteen%20has%20increasingly%20sounded%20off%20about%20the%20presidential%20administrations%20of%20Donald%20J.%20Trump.%20Asked%20during%20a%20cover-story%20interview%20with%20Variety%20in%202017%20why%20he%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20been%20more%20critical%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWell%2C%20if%20you%20read%20Charles%20Blow%20in%20The%20New%20York%20Times%2C%20he%20carries%20the%20flag%20pretty%20well.%20I%E2%80%99m%20ambivalent%20about%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Jem%20Aswad%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2025%2Fmusic%2Fnews%2Fbruce-springsteen-calls-trump-corrupt-incompetent-treasonous-1236398433%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Waymo%20recalled%20software%20for%20more%20than%201%2C200%20robotaxis%20after%20several%20cars%20were%20involved%20in%20collisions%20with%20barriers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22911%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Waymo%20fleet%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6824fc4cc6ad288d1480f5a4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWaymo%20issued%20a%20software%20recall%20to%20more%20than%201%2C200%20robotaxis%20after%20several%20incidents%20involving%20collisions%20with%20roadway%20barriers.%3Cp%3EPatrick%20T.%20Fallon%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EWaymo%20issued%20a%20software%20recall%20for%20more%20than%201%2C200%20robotaxis%2C%20a%20NHTSA%20report%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20recall%20was%20in%20response%20to%20several%20incidents%20where%20Waymo's%20cars%20collided%20with%20%26quot%3Bchains%20or%20gates.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThis%20is%20Waymo's%20third%20recall%20in%20more%20than%20a%20year.%20The%20last%20two%20were%20voluntary.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwaymo%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EWaymo%3C%2Fa%3E%20issued%20a%20software%20recall%20for%20its%20robotaxi%20fleet%20of%20about%201%2C212%20cars%20after%20several%20of%20them%20ran%20into%20objects%20such%20as%20gates%20and%20chains%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20filed%20with%20the%20National%20Highway%20Traffic%20Safety%20Administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20NHTSA%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20an%20email%20that%20the%20agency%20opened%20an%20inquiry%20into%20Waymo's%20fifth-generation%20driver%20last%20year%20after%20receiving%2022%20incident%20reports%2C%20some%20of%20which%20included%20collisions%20with%20stationary%20and%20semi-stationary%20roadway%20barriers.%20The%20spokesperson%20said%20the%20investigation%20remains%20open.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20NHTSA%20report%20said%20the%20incidents%20involving%20collisions%20into%20the%20barriers%20occurred%20between%20December%202022%20and%20April%202024.%20There%20were%20no%20injuries%20involved%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20report%2C%20Waymo%20also%20flagged%20to%20NHTSA%20nine%20other%20minor%20collisions%20with%20similar%20barriers%20that%20occurred%20between%20February%202024%20and%20December%202024.%20By%20the%20time%20NHTSA%20opened%20the%20inquiry%2C%20Waymo%20said%20that%20it%20had%20been%20working%20on%20a%20software%20update%2C%20according%20to%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20software%20update%20was%20fully%20rolled%20out%20for%20Waymo's%20entire%20fleet%20by%20December%202024.%20It%20does%20not%20impact%20Waymo's%20current%20operations%2C%20a%20Waymo%20spokesperson%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20an%20email.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWaymo%20provides%20more%20than%20250%2C000%20paid%20trips%20every%20week%20in%20some%20of%20the%20most%20challenging%20driving%20environments%20in%20the%20US%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BWe%20hold%20ourselves%20to%20a%20high%20safety%20standard%2C%20and%20our%20record%20of%20reducing%20injuries%20over%20tens%20of%20millions%20of%20fully%20autonomous%20miles%20driven%20shows%20our%20technology%20is%20making%20roads%20safer.%20NHTSA%20plays%20a%20vital%20role%20in%20road%20safety%2C%20and%20we%20will%20continue%20to%20work%20collaboratively%20with%20the%20agency%20as%20part%20of%20our%20mission%20to%20be%20the%20world's%20most%20trusted%20driver.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20third%20recall%20Waymo%20has%20issued%20in%20little%20more%20than%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20February%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E2024%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwaymo-issues-recall-two-cars-crashed-into-same-pickup-truck-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EWaymo%20issued%20a%20voluntary%20recall%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20more%20than%20400%20vehicles%20after%20two%20of%20its%20robotaxis%20crashed%20into%20a%20pickup%20truck%20that%20was%20being%20towed.%20The%20crash%20caused%20only%20minor%20vehicle%20damage%2C%20and%20no%20passengers%20were%20involved.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20issued%20another%20voluntary%20recall%20in%20June%202024%20for%20more%20than%20670%20cars%20after%20an%20unoccupied%20Waymo%20crashed%20into%20a%20telephone%20pole%20in%20Phoenix%2C%20according%20to%20NHTSA%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20recalls%20involved%20software%20updates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWaymo%20has%20said%20that%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwaymo-driverless-cars-data-safer-than-human-driven-vehicles-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erobotaxis%20are%20safer%20than%20human%20drivers%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Data%20published%20by%20the%20company%20showed%20that%20Waymo's%20cars%20saw%2081%25%20%26quot%3Bfewer%20injury-causing%20crashes%26quot%3B%20than%20the%20average%20human%20driver%20when%20comparing%20millions%20of%20miles%20Waymo%20has%20driven%20in%20Phoenix%20and