nket%20to%20keep%20the%20weight%20evenly%20distributed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Weighted%20Comforter%20comes%20in%20white%20and%20a%20soft%20gray%20with%20loops%20to%20add%20your%20own%20duvet%20cover.%20The%20blanket%20version%20is%20also%20available%20in%20navy%20and%20green.%20Due%20to%20its%20size%2C%20the%20comforter%20should%20only%20be%20washed%20at%20a%20commercial%20laundromat.%20The%20blankets%2C%20in%20throws%20and%20queen%20size%2C%20may%20be%20able%20to%20be%20washed%20at%20home%20in%20your%20normal%20machine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226e78f3de-0ebe-4dc8-beda-6280dcd3c13c%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Our%20review%20of%20the%20Baloo%20Weighted%20Comforter%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EOur%20review%20of%20the%20Baloo%20Weighted%20Comforter%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Baloo%20weighted%20comforter%20sits%20in%20a%20canvas%20bag%20on%20a%20couch.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F682203753fe8d39283658d4b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBaloo's%20Weighted%20Comforter%20comes%20in%20a%20canvas%20tote%20for%20easy%20storage.%3Cp%3EKinsley%20Searles%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Weighted%20Comforter%20comes%20packaged%20in%20a%20sturdy%2C%20reusable%20canvas%20bag.%20I%20appreciated%20this%20detail%20because%20it%20makes%20storage%20easy.%20I%20noticed%20right%20away%20that%20it%20was%20made%20with%20high-quality%20material.%20The%20cotton%20was%20crisp%20and%20smooth%2C%20like%20percale%20sheets%20or%20a%20freshly%20ironed%20button-down%20shirt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20tried%20the%20king-size%20blanket%2C%20which%20weighs%20in%20at%2025%20pounds.%20Even%20though%20this%20was%20a%20hefty%20blanket%2C%20I%20made%20the%20bed%20relatively%20easily.%20I%20also%20love%20to%20tug%20at%20the%20blankets%20throughout%20the%20night%20until%20they%20fit%20snugly%20under%20my%20chin.%20I%20had%20no%20problems%20moving%20the%20blanket%20as%20I%20fell%20asleep.%20It's%20also%20one%20of%20the%20few%20weighted%20blankets%20that%20are%20fit%20for%20sharing%2C%20since%20it's%20designed%20to%20drape%20over%20the%20side%20of%20the%20bed.%20My%20partner%20and%20I%20never%20fought%20over%20the%20blankets%20at%20night%2C%20and%20we%20both%20woke%20up%20feeling%20refreshed%20and%20well-rested.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20like%20it%20when%20my%20weighted%20blanket%20feels%20like%20sleeping%20under%20a%20beanbag.%20Thankfully%2C%20Baloo's%20weighted%20comforter%20gives%20an%20evenly%20distributed%20weighted%20feel%20without%20the%20distinct%20feeling%20of%20glass%20beads.%20I%20also%20appreciated%20that%20the%20weight%20was%20centered%20in%20the%20middle%2C%20because%20it%20helped%20the%20comforter%20fully%20envelop%20my%20body%20in%20a%20nice%2C%20tight%20hug.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20initially%20been%20a%20little%20skeptical%20of%20the%20claim%20that%20weighted%20blankets%20could%20help%20you%20sleep%20better%20at%20night.%20After%20researching%20these%20products%20and%20using%20Baloo's%20weighted%20comforter%2C%20I'm%20a%20believer.%20The%20slight%20pressure%20from%20the%20weighted%20comforter%20eases%20me%20to%20sleep%20and%20helps%20me%20stay%20asleep%20throughout%20the%20night.%20I%20love%20feeling%20snuggled%20tightly%20all%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20being%20called%20a%20comforter%2C%20it%20lacks%20the%20thick%2C%20fluffy%20feel%20of%20a%20traditional%20down%20or%20down-alternative%20comforter.%20The%20blanket%20itself%20is%20only%20filled%20with%20glass%20beads%20so%20that%20you%20won't%20get%20a%20cushy%20feel%20from%20polyfiber%20or%20down%20filling.%20The%20lack%20of%20soft%20filling%20does%20mean%20that%20the%20weight%20is%20more%20pronounced%2C%20but%20I%20missed%20feeling%20like%20being%20surrounded%20by%20a%20cloud.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20the%20comforter's%20thinness%20also%20lends%20itself%20well%20to%20its%20cooling%20and%20breathability.