%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223574%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hasbro%20sign%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6824c2f4c6ad288d1480eabc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222383%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Hasbro%20executive%20said%20the%20company%20halted%20price%20increases%20and%20production%20changes%20after%20Trump%20announced%20a%20deal%20with%20China.%3Cp%3EJonathan%20Wiggs%2FThe%20Boston%20Globe%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20Hasbro%20exec%20said%20the%20company's%20plans%20drastically%20changed%20after%20tariffs%20on%20China%20were%20paused.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20said%20the%20company%20halted%20pricing%20changes%20and%20plans%20to%20halt%20some%20production%20entirely.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EStill%2C%20the%20toymaker%20exec%20said%20the%20environment%20is%20uncertain%20and%20%26quot%3Bevery%20day%20is%20a%20new%20adventure.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%2C%20the%20toy%20maker%20Hasbro%20was%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Epreparing%20big%20changes%20to%20contend%20with%20triple-digit%20tariffs%20on%20Chinese%20imports.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20Monday%2C%20all%20of%20those%20calculations%20were%20different.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGina%20Goetter%2C%20Hasbro's%20Chief%20Financial%20Officer%20and%20Chief%20Operating%20Officer%2C%20said%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump'%3C%2Fa%3Es%20decision%20to%20temporarily%20lower%20tariffs%20on%20China%20from%20145%25%20to%2030%25%20drastically%20altered%20the%20company's%20plans.%20She%20called%20the%20announcement%20a%20%26quot%3Bpleasant%20surprise%26quot%3B%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjpmorgan-columbus-ohio-polaris-first-week-rto-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EJP%20Morgan's%3C%2Fa%3E%20Technology%2C%20Media%2C%20and%20Communications%20Conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3