%20There's%20also%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Figamingbusiness.com%2Fsports-betting%2Fonline-sports-betting%2Fsafe-bet-act-reintroduce%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erenewed%20effort%3C%2Fa%3E%20this%20year%20to%20introduce%20federal%20regulations%20on%20gambling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20expansion%20of%20online%20casino%20legislation%20has%20screeched%20to%20a%20halt%2C%20leaving%20operators%20wondering%20where%20their%20next%20phase%20of%20growth%20will%20come%20from.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20new%20entrants%20and%20ways%20to%20risk%20money%20like%20sports%20predictions%20and%20sweepstakes%20casinos%20are%20disrupting%20the%20landscape%20%E2%80%94%20and%20drawing%20regulatory%20scrutiny.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20industry%20insiders%20said%20it%20feels%20like%20these%20issues%2C%20which%20have%20been%20brewing%20for%20the%20last%20year%20or%20more%2C%20are%20all%20coming%20to%20a%20head%20in%202025.%20These%20key%20battlegrounds%20could%20define%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fonline-gambling-conference-next-summit-takeaways-ai-predictions-sweepstakes-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efuture%20of%20the%20gambling%20industry%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20consumer%20protections.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223daa6990-abfc-4148-ad2a-394107550505%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESports%20predictions%20could%20create%20a%20pathway%20to%20betting%20across%20the%20country%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPrediction%20markets%20are%20sucking%20up%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20oxygen%20in%20the%20room%20right%20now%2C%20five%20industry%20insiders%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20markets%20let%20users%20across%20the%20country%20put%20money%20on%20potential%20winners%20of%20certain%20sporting%20events.%20Consumers%20can%20go%20on%20a%20website%20like%20Kalshi%20to%20%26quot%3Bpredict%26quot%3B%20who%20will%20win%20a%20series%20in%20the%20NBA%20playoffs%2C%20for%20example.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nikola%20Jokic%20drives%20to%20the%20net%20in%20a%20playoff%20game%20between%20the%20Denver%20Nuggets%20and%20the%20Oklahoma%20City%20Thunder%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6824d57668a29290080150d7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKalshi%20users%20can%20predict%20who%20will%20win%20a%20game%2C%20such%20as%20the%20playoff%20matchup%20between%20the%20Denver%20Nuggets%20and%20Oklahoma%20City%20Thunder.%3Cp%3EJoshua%20Gateley%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20markets%20are%20being%20run%20by%20commodities%20and%20financial%20platforms%2C%20rather%20than%20gambling%20operators.%20But%20Kalshi%20and%20some%20other%20companies%20offering%20sports%20predictions%20have%20received%20cease%20and%20desist%20orders%20this%20year%20from%20gambling%20regulators%20in%20several%20states%2C%20including%20Nevada%20and%20New%20Jersey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKalshi%20has%20taken%20the%20issue%20to%20the%20courts%2C%20arguing%20that%20it's%20regulated%20by%20the%20federal%20Commodity%20Futures%20Trading%20Commission%2C%20not%20these%20state%20gambling%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20legal%20fights%20appear%20to%20be%20going%20Kalshi's%20way.%20The%20federal%20courts%20in%20Nevada%20and%20New%20Jersey%20have%20so%20far%20sided%20with%20Kalshi%20and%20blocked%20the%20cease-and-desists.%20This%20month%2C%20the%20CTFC%20also%20dropped%20an%20earlier%20appeal%20against%20the%20company's%20election%20predictions%2C%20signaling%20that%20the%20commission%20has%20a%20favorable%20view%20on%20prediction%20markets%20overall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKalshi%20has%20won%20a%20couple%20of%20early%20rounds%2C%20but%20it%20is%20still%20early%20in%20the%20fight%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20James%20Kilsby%2C%20chief%20analyst%20at%20Vixio%2C%20a%20regulatory%20tech%20company%20that%20works%20with%20the%20gambling%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20big%20question%20is%20how%20much%20fight%20the%20states%20have%20in%20them.%20The%20answer%20will%20likely%20tie%20back%20to%20how%20much%20tax%20revenue%20they%20risk%20losing%2C%20said%20Andrew%20Kim%2C%20an%20appellate%20and%20gaming%20litigator%20at%20Goodwin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKalshi%20and%20other%20sports%20prediction%20markets%20offer%20a%20very%20narrow%20product.%20So%20far%2C%20these%20platforms%20don't%20offer%20parlays%20or%20prop%20bets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20definitely%20a%20path%20where%20all%20of%20that%20grows%20and%20becomes%20bigger%20and%20becomes%20an%20actual%20threat%20to%20the%20regime%20of%20sports%20betting%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Dustin%20Gouker%2C%20a%20gaming%20industry%20consultant%20who%20follows%20prediction%20markets%20closely%20in%20his%20Closing%20Line%20newsletter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20sports%20predictions%20are%20cleared%20to%20continue%2C%20prediction%20markets%20could%20create%20a%20path%20for%20gambling%20companies%20to%20operate%20in%20all%2050%20states.%20Gambling%20operators%20DraftKings%20and%20FanDuel%20told%20investors%20on%20recent%20earnings%20calls%20that%20they're%20interested%20in%20a%20prediction%20market%20product.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20in%20the%20industry%20at%20the%20moment%20are%20very%20much%20in%20a%20wait-and-see%20mode%20on%20this%20one%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Steve%20Ruddock%2C%20a%20gambling%20industry%20analyst%20and%20consultant.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20everybody%20needs%20to%20be%20concerned%20about%20in%20the%20industry%20is%20being%20left%20behind.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2234982661-e5b4-4545-a64f-40f50ec5e1df%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESweepstakes%20casinos%20are%20under%20siege%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20early%20momentum%20for%20sports%20predictions%20suggests%20they%20may%20be%20here%20to%20stay%2C%20the%20future%20of%20online%20sweepstakes%20is%20less%20certain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20games%2C%20from%20sites%20like%20Chumba%20Casino%20and%20McLuck%2C%20can%20resemble%20slots%2C%20table%20games%2C%20or%20sports%20betting%2C%20but%20they%20allow%20players%20to%20play%20for%20free%20and%20win%20digital%20coins%20that%20can%20be%20exchanged%20for%20cash.%20Users%20can%20typically%20also%20buy%20and%20wager%20these%20coins%2C%20which%20is%20where%20the%20line%20between%20sweepstakes%20and%20a%20regular%20online%20casino%20really%20starts%20to%20blur.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20states%2C%20including%20New%20York%2C%20Connecticut%2C%20Illinois%2C%20and%20Montana%2C%20are%20considering%20banning%20them.%20New%20York's%20bill%20would%20make%20it%20illegal%20to%20operate%2C%20promote%2C%20or%20support%20these%20businesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFlorida%20and%20a%20few%20other%20states%20also%20considered%20bills%20rejecting%20these%20games%2C%20but%20those%20efforts%20have%20either%20failed%20or%20stalled.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20industry%20is%20very%20focused%20on%20sweepstakes%20operations%2C%26quot%3B%20Kilsby%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat%20is%20very%20much%20a%20major%20policy%20issue%20of%202025%20that%20wasn't%20really%20the%20case%20in%20previous%20years.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20big%20deal%20in%20the%20industry%20because%20these%20games%20are%20regulated%20differently%20from%20online%20casino%20games%2C%C2%A0which%20can%20make%20them%20available%20to%20a%20wider%20set%20of%20consumers.%20Some%2C%20like%20a%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsbcamericas.com%2F2025%2F02%2F10%2Fhigh-5-games-damages-casino-verdict%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWashington%20court%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20say%20they're%20illegal%20gambling.%20Others%20argue%20they're%20simply%20innovating%20in%20a%20common%20gaming%20category%3A%20sweepstakes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20recent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legalsportsreport.com%2F214658%2Flawsuit-targets-sweeps-operator-vgw-apple-google-for-alleged-illegal-gambling%2F%3Futm_source%3Dchatgpt.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elawsuits%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20been%20filed%20against%20sweepstakes%20operators.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2229ab3b88-3279-418e-a9ef-a5d856e378de%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ERewriting%20the%20rules%20%E2%80%94%20and%20taxes%20%E2%80%94%20for%20gambling%20companies%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELawsuits%20against%20gambling%20companies%20are%20also%20piling%20up%20in%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENew%20cases%20are%20challenging%20marketing%20and%20promotional%20practices%2C%20such%20as%20VIP%20programs%20and%20certain%20bonus%20offers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBaltimore%20City%2C%20for%20example%2C%20sued%20DraftKings%20and%20FanDuel%20in%20April%20over%20what%20it%20alleged%20are%20%26quot%3Bpredatory%20practices.%26quot%3B%20The%20complaint%20called%20out%20both%20%26quot%3Bbonus%20bets%26quot%3B%20and%20VIP%20programs%2C%20which%20are%20loyalty%20plays%20that%20the%20complaint%20says%20%26quot%3Bpersonalize%20the%20inducements%20to%20gamble.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECustomers%20sue%20gambling%20operators%20all%20the%20time%20%E2%80%94%20cases%20like%20these%20aren't%20new%20to%20the%20industry.%20But%20the%20%26quot%3Btidal%20wave%26quot%3B%20of%20recent%20consumer%20litigation%20could%20be%20a%20beachhead%20of%20a%20broader%20pushback%2C%20said%20Kim%20at%20Goodwin%2C%20who%20thinks%20the%20industry%20will%20likely%20see%20more%20of%20these%20lawsuits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20hard%20to%20tell%20what%20the%20lasting%20impact%20will%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKilsby%20said%20it's%20common%20for%20countries%20to%20experience%20a%20%26quot%3Bregulatory%20reset%26quot%3B%20after%20a%20period%20of%20%26quot%3Bliberalization%26quot%3B%20in%20regulated%20online%20gambling.%20A%20similar%20trend%20has%20played%20out%20in%20markets%20across%20Europe%2C%20with%20some%20countries%20imposing%20strict%20restrictions%20on%20gambling%20ads%2C%20for%20example.%20He%20pointed%20to%20US%20states%20like%20New%20York%2C%20New%20Jersey%2C%20and%20Illinois%20revisiting%20their%20gambling%20regulations%2C%20but%20said%20we've%20not%20yet%20seen%20efforts%20that%20have%20%26quot%3Bdramatically%20redrawn%20the%20landscape.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20this%20is%20a%20very%20universal%20dynamic%20for%20the%20industry%2C%20it's%20a%20very%20fair%20question%20to%20ask%3A%20How%20does%20the%20same%20trend%20play%20out%20in%20North%20America%3F%26quot%3B%20Kilsby%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20state%20regulators%20are%20also%20ratcheting%20up%20taxes%20on%20gambling%20and%20sports%20betting%20companies%2C%20as%20Kilsby%20and%20Grove%20pointed%20out.%20New%20Jersey's%20governor%2C%20for%20one%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.covers.com%2Findustry%2Fnew-jersey-governor-propose-tax-hike-sports-betting-igaming-february-2025%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eproposed%3C%2Fa%3E%20hiking%20the%20tax%20rate%20for%20online%20gambling%20to%2025%25.%20Ohio's%20governor%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdeadspin.com%2Flegal-betting%2Fohio-governor-looks-to-double-sports-betting-tax%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eproposed%3C%2Fa%3E%20doubling%20its%20tax%20rate%20on%20sports%20betting%20to%2040%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flegal-battles-reshaping-us-gambling-industry-2025-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1747245079000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6824caad68a2929008014e7c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flegal-battles-reshaping-us-gambling-industry-2025-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Gambling%20is%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20revenue%20streams%20to%20some%20states%2C%20but%20it%20has%20recently%20come%20under%20fire%20with%20several%20lawsuits%20in%20a%20handful%20of%20locales.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22arodriguez%40businessinsider.com%20(Ashley%20Rodriguez%2CMackenzie%20Meaney)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A27%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flegal-battles-reshaping-us-gambling-industry-2025-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpU