20employees%20in%20storing%2C%20picking%2C%20packing%2C%20and%20shipping%20goods.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20roughly%20a%20decade%2C%20Amazon's%20head%20count%20grew%20massively%2C%20even%20though%20it%20was%20embracing%20automation.%20But%20this%20has%20gone%20into%20reverse%20in%20recent%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20doubling%20its%20workforce%20to%201.6%20million%20between%202019%20and%202021%2C%20Amazon's%20head%20count%20declined%20to%201.55%20million%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221846%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20chart%20showing%20Amazon%20headcount%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6824cf3668a2929008014f96%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22847%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAmazon's%20head%20count.%3Cp%3EAmazon%20public%20filings%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221115f1df-761d-4600-8700-c5666d4e21af%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHumans%20working%20alongside%20robots%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%20introduced%20Vulcan%20last%20week%20as%20its%20first%20tactile%20robot.%20It's%20capable%20of%20sensing%20and%20adjusting%20the%20force%20needed%20to%20pick%20products%20from%20crowded%20bins%20and%20tall%20baskets%2C%20improving%20safety%20and%20speed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20internal%20document%20obtained%20by%20BI%2C%20Amazon's%20robotics%20team%20is%20working%20on%20at%20least%20two%20AI%20models%20intended%20to%20be%20building%20blocks%20for%20new%20applications%20that%20%26quot%3Bwill%20significantly%20enhance%20the%20efficiency%20and%20responsiveness%20of%20our%20robotics%20systems.%26quot%3B%20The%20company%20is%20also%20working%20on%20a%20new%20AI%20model%20called%20%26quot%3BTetris%2C%26quot%3B%20aimed%20at%20reducing%20variable%20labor%20and%20transportation%20costs%2C%20the%20document%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20document%2C%20Aaron%20Parness%2C%20the%20director%20of%20applied%20science%20at%20Amazon%20Robotics%2C%20emphasized%20robots'%20role%20in%20enhancing%20efficiency%20and%20safety%20to%20ultimately%20enable%20the%20company%20to%20fulfill%20more%20orders%20and%20deliver%20more%20shipments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20always%20envisioned%20a%20solution%20that's%20robots%20and%20humans%20working%20side%20by%20side%2C%26quot%3B%20Parness%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20we%20think%20the%20sum%20of%20the%20two%20together%20is%20better%20than%20the%20parts%20alone.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20automation%20helps%20Amazon%20retain%20frontline%20employees%20in%20a%20competitive%20labor%20market%20by%20improving%20the%20work%20environment%20and%20offering%20new%20technical%20career%20paths%20in%20maintenance%20and%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20be%20competitive%20for%20workers%2C%26quot%3B%20Parness%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bso%20that%20people%20will%20want%20to%20work%20and%20stay%20at%20Amazon.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f240e5a6-bf07-4d40-b0ca-915d9f9580f6%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20potential%20solution%20for%20labor%20shortages%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20Amazon%20employees%20told%20BI%20that%20machines%20such%20as%20Vulcan%20are%20designed%20not%20only%20to%20enhance%20productivity%20but%20also%20to%20help%20address%20a%20growing%20labor%20gap.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20employee%20said%20the%20company%20had%20set%20aggressive%20targets%20to%20automate%20much%20of%20the%20warehouse%20workload%20over%20the%20next%20decade%20to%20drive%20down%20costs.%20Amazon%20is%20also%20extensively%20researching%20how%20to%20upskill%20the%20current%20workforce%20to%20move%20them%20into%20more%20maintenance-related%20jobs%2C%20this%20person%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20Amazon's%20continued%20growth%2C%20finding%20enough%20workers%20has%20become%20increasingly%20difficult%2C%20another%20Amazon%20insider%20told%20BI.%20If%20the%20company%20doesn't%20automate%20more%2C%20it%20will%20struggle%20to%20keep%20up%20with%20demand%2C%20this%20person%20added