ia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FIMG_2436-1_11zon-1747034802-150x200.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FIMG_2436-1_11zon-1747034802.jpg%20768w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-427028%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CI%20always%20want%20to%20ensure%20my%20baby%20experiences%20all%20kinds%20of%20things%20%E2%80%94%20different%20cuisines%2C%20or%20going%20out%20to%20social%20spaces%2C%E2%80%9D%20Saumya%20says.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20list%20was%20a%20lifeline%20%E2%80%94%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9Cwhat%20groceries%20I%20am%20supposed%20to%20buy%20for%20that%20day%2C%20how%20much%20milk%20I%20must%20pump%20for%20my%20baby%2C%20how%20much%20I%20had%20pumped%20during%20the%20day%2C%20when%20is%20the%20next%20feed%20and%20so%20much%20more%2C%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229253875046%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CMom%E2%80%99s%20brain%20works%20like%20this%3A%20We%20think%20of%20doing%20one%20task%20and%20the%20next%20minute%20we%20forget%20it.%20That%E2%80%99s%20how%20it%20has%20always%20been%20for%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%20she%20laughs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20her%20calendar%20is%20packed%2C%20her%20heart%20is%20full.%20Whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20planning%20new%20meals%20or%20bedtime%20cuddles%2C%20Saumya%20is%20determined%20to%20make%20every%20day%20meaningful%20for%20her%20daughter.%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CCurrently%20I%20always%20want%20to%20ensure%20my%20baby%20experiences%20all%20kinds%20of%20things%20%E2%80%94%20it%20can%20be%20different%20cuisines%2C%20or%20going%20out%20to%20social%20spaces.%20I%20just%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20her%20to%20be%20stuck%20in%20betwe