is%20business%2C%20I%20relied%20heavily%20on%20my%20mother-in-law%2C%20brother-in-law%2C%20and%20Chitra%20with%20the%20baby%E2%80%99s%20work.%20And%20today%20I%20can%20tell%20it%20was%20the%20three%20of%20them%20who%20raised%20my%20daughter%20while%20I%20took%20care%20of%20the%20home%2C%20made%20meals%20for%20all%2C%20and%20did%20all%20the%20household%20chores%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Bhavani.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-54-1747035200.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mother%20day%20mental%20load%20on%20moms%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-54-1747035200.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-54-1747035200-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-54-1747035200-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-54-1747035200-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-54-1747035200-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-427035%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EFrom%20brewing%20coffee%20to%20feeding%20the%20dog%2C%20Bhavani%20and%20Chitra%20stayed%20on%20their%20feet%2C%20while%20others%20looked%20after%20the%20little%20ones.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20never%20just%20one%20person%20doing%20it%20all%E2%80%94someone%20was%20always%20around%20to%20lend%20a%20hand.%20While%20Bhavani%20focused%20on%20her%20baby%20and%20managed%20the%20kitchen%2C%20Chitra%20took%20care%20of%20everything%20else%E2%80%94often%20without%20stopping%20